            "highlight": "First",
            "keywords": "on time, not late",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p1_2",
            "text": "Second, we have to wear the school uniform every day.",
            "emoji": "👕",
            "highlight": "Second",
            "keywords": "wear uniform",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p1_3",
            "text": "Third, we can't eat snacks or use phones in the classroom.",
            "emoji": "🚫",
            "highlight": "Third",
            "keywords": "no snacks, no phones",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p2",
        "text": "We also have to follow some other rules.",
        "emoji": "📜",
        "highlight": "also",
        "keywords": "follow rules",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p2_1",
            "text": "We mustn't run in the hallways or litter.",
            "emoji": "🚶",
            "keywords": "not run, not litter",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_2",
            "text": "We should be polite and treat everyone with respect.",
            "emoji": "🤝",
            "keywords": "polite, respect",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
